  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A statement from Russia about the situation in this country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The spokesperson of the Russian Ministry of Foreign Affairs Mrs. Maria Zakharova said that the current situation in Sri Lanka is an internal matter of Sri Lanka.",
        "Mrs. Maria Sakharova stated that Sri Lanka is a friendly state of Russia and that the political process of Sri Lanka will continue in accordance with the existing laws and constitution of the country and that Russia believes that the new administration will take the necessary measures to rescue Sri Lanka from the current economic crisis.",
        "Mrs. Sakharova said that she hopes that the current situation in Sri Lanka will return to normal soon."
      ],
